<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 miàn duì zāi nán zhàn huǒ, wǒ néng zuò shén me? rén men liú lí shī suǒ, wǒ néng zuò shén me?
 shì jiè rú cǐ xié è, wǒ néng zuò shén me? tóng bāo yuǎn lí zhēn shén, wǒ néng zuò shén me?
 zhǔ a zhǔ a wǒ yào duì nǐ shuō, huà yǔ wèi chū, lèi shuǐ yǐ dī luò,,
 qiú nǐ lái yǐn dǎo wǒ qiú nǐ lái bāng zhù wǒ, wǒ zhēn de yuàn yì wèi nǐ ér huó,
 huó chū nǐ nà wú sī de ài, huó chū nǐ nà róng měi de pǐn gé,
 huó chū nǐ de shùn fú qiān bēi shě jǐ, yīn wèi nǐ wǒ cái huó zhe!</lyrics>
<title>wǒ néng zuò shén me 迦南1384</title>
